      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. Featuring unblemished coachwork and an interior that remains in factory-original state, this motorcar has been curated with the highest standards of care. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically superior, it represents a premier acquisition for the most discerning automotive enthusiast.",
