    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied it since day one and it's in absolutely pristine shape. No scratches, the interior still has that fresh feel, and it drives like an absolute dream! I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
