    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-grade A80 chassis, powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six. This specimen retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup, exhibiting perfect boost pressure regulation and zero shaft play. Power is routed through the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. The undercarriage is immaculate, with all bushings, double-wishbone suspension components, and four-piston braking calipers maintained to exacting OEM standards. Free of any heat-cycle degradation or fluid seepage, this numbers-matching vehicle represents the pinnacle of Japanese grand touring engineering and remains in showroom-fresh mechanical order.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records available. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and its condition is absolutely impeccable. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections across the bodywork. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of creases or bolster wear, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and a powertrain that delivers smooth, effortless performance. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a peak-condition example of this model. The sale includes all original manuals, two keys, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 48900.0,
